{
  "name": "FirstAI 08 — Daily Standup Aggregator",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Live deployment checklist\n\nWorkflow: FirstAI 08 — Daily Standup Aggregator\nNodes: 6\nTrigger: Daily 9am\nCredentials/services: Linear API, OpenAI, Slack OAuth\nPlaceholders: #standup, YOUR_ORG, YOUR_REPO\nEnvironment variables: LINEAR_API_KEY\nExternal webhook setup: not required\n\nBefore activating:\n1. Configure every credential in n8n Credentials.\n2. Replace every placeholder above with live IDs, channels, folders, or database IDs.\n3. Execute once with test data and inspect every node output.\n4. Activate only after the workflow reaches its final node successfully.",
        "height": 440,
        "width": 520,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "live-a6b821a75402d82eb64ec222",
      "name": "Live Deployment Checklist",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        80,
        -140
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "cronExpression",
              "expression": "0 9 * * 1-5"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "5bbf059d-b41a-409b-a455-e0614e1cc2ac",
      "name": "Daily 9am",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [
        240,
        300
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "https://api.linear.app/graphql",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "Authorization",
              "value": "={{ $env.LINEAR_API_KEY }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "sendBody": true,
        "jsonBody": "={\n  \"query\": \"{ issues(filter:{updatedAt:{gte:\\\"{{ $now.minus({days:1}).toISO() }}\\\"}}){ nodes{ title state{name} assignee{name} } } }\"\n}"
      },
      "id": "dc4e215a-f567-4c41-8bac-87ba10ff5348",
      "name": "Linear Updates",
